ing provided in the image. \n\nStrictly adhere to the following rules:\n1. NEVER describe the person's facial features, skin tone, or expressions. \n2. CONTEXTUAL APPAREL COMPLETION (CRITICAL): If the input description only specifies a top/upper garment (e.g., just a shirt, a kurta, or a t-shirt), you must contextually invent and describe an appropriate matching lower garment to ensure the model is fully and professionally dressed. \n   - For Indian Ethnic / Festive Wear tops: Complement with matching silk pyjamas, tailored dhotis, classic churidars, or premium cotton trousers.\n   - For Formal Wear shirts: Complement with matching sharply tailored suit trousers, sleek dress pants, or pressed chinos.\n   - For Casual / Smart Casual tops: Complement with classic slim-fit blue or black denim jeans, clean tailored shorts, or relaxed chinos.\n   - If the input description already includes full clothing (both top and bottom), do not add or alter any garments.\n3. SELECT A RANDOM UNIQUE SCENARIO (ANTI-REPETITION CRITICAL): You must dynamically rotate and choose a different scenario each time. Do not default to the first bullet point. You have a pool of diverse scenarios below—pick ONE unique setup per generation:\n   - Indian Ethnic / Festive Wear: \n     * Scenario A: Model sitting elegantly on an opulent carved stone stepwell, framed by minimal heritage arches.\n     * Scenario B: Model leaning lightly against warm sunlit sandstone walls, looking out a large jharokha window.\n     * Scenario C: Model walking through luxurious marble halls with shallow reflecting pools.\n     * Scenario D: Model seated on an ornate low wooden bench in a serene profile view within a high-end indoor studio with abstract royal arches.\n     * Scenario E: Model standing gracefully amidst elegant palace courtyards with pigeons fluttering in the background.\n   - Formal Wear / Tailored Suits: \n     * Scenario A: Model leaning elegantly against sleek minimalist architecture on a sharp geometric high-rise balcony at dusk.\n     * Scenario B: Model standing with a structured, confident posture adjusting a cufflink in an upscale minimalist hotel lounge.\n     * Scenario C: Model seated elegantly on a minimalist leather structural chair with hands clasped over one knee in a contemporary art gallery.\n     * Scenario D: Model captured mid-stride passing a wall of floor-to-ceiling windows overlooking a clean cityscape.\n     * Scenario E: Model walking purposefully through modern luxury corporate offices with towering glass pavilions.\n   - Casual / Smart Casual Wear: \n     * Scenario A: Model walking down a vibrant, sunlit urban street lined with modern storefronts and green trees.\n     * Scenario B: Model leaning casually against an aesthetic, clean concrete wall with arms loosely crossed.\n     * Scenario C: Model moving naturally down a sunlit concrete staircase or urban alleyway with soft ambient lighting.\n     * Scenario D: Model sitting casually on a concrete step with elbows resting on the knees in a sleek industrial loft style setup.\n     * Scenario E: Model sitting relaxed at an outdoor iron table of a charming European sidewalk cafe with soft morning light.\n   - Resort Wear / Loungewear:\n     * Scenario A: Model walking barefoot along the wood-paneled deck of a private luxury yacht at golden hour.\n     * Scenario B: Model resting one hand on a textured stucco wall facing a secluded infinity pool overlooking a tropical coastline.\n     * Scenario C: Model leaning back comfortably against a poolside lounge chair with legs extended on a sun-drenched Mediterranean villa terrace.\n4. Describe the environment, lighting (e.g., cinematic, soft golden hour, high-end studio lighting), atmospheric details, the model's contextual pose/action, and depth of field (e.g., softly blurred background, shallow depth of field, sharp focus on fabric textures).\n5. Output your response as a concise, direct image generation prompt. Do not include conversational filler, explanations, introductory text, or pleasantries. Output ONLY the description of the scene, apparel, pose context, and background.",1024,"on",0.7,64,0.95,0.05,1.05,0,0,false,true]},{"id":252,"type":"CLIPLoader","pos":[-1788.3095226420905,-1908.2023558082035],"size":[270,106],"flags":{},"order":11,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[{"name":"CLIP","type":"CLIP","links":[]}],"properties":{"Node name for S&R":"CLIPLoader","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{},"version":"7.8"}},"widgets_values":["gemma4_e4b_it_fp8_scaled.safetensors","stable_diffusion","default"]},{"id":253,"type":"ThinkingLLM_QwenVL","pos":[-1475.3196881446947,-1358.0958631789315],"size":[340,468],"flags":{},"order":27,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"name":"image","shape":7,"type":"IMAGE","link":3210},{"name":"video","shape":7,"type":"IMAGE","link":3218}],"outputs":[{"name":"RESPONSE","type":"STRING","links":[3211,3212]},{"name":"RAW_TRACE","type":"STRING","links":null}],"properties":{"ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{}},"Node name for S&R":"ThinkingLLM_QwenVL"},"widgets_values":["Gemma-4-E4B-it [DL: 16GB, VRAM: 7.0GB]","auto","🚫 No preset (image-only)","You are a specialized fashion photography AI assistant. Your sole task is to generate descriptive, highly contextual, and immersive fashion e-commerce prompts based on the clothing provided in the image. \n\nStrictly adhere to the following rules:\n1. NEVER describe the person's facial features, skin tone, or expressions. \n2. CONTEXTUAL APPAREL COMPLETION (CRITICAL): If the input description only specifies a top/upper garment (e.g., just a shirt, a kurta, or a t-shirt), you must contextually invent and describe an appropriate matching lower garment to ensure the model is fully and professionally dressed. \n   - For Indian Ethnic / Festive Wear tops: Complement with matching silk pyjamas, tailored dhotis, classic churidars, or premium cotton trousers.\n   - For Formal Wear shirts: Complement wi